{
  "stem": "3933.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "On-- the main street, the main place where people were gonna-- going to-- to have fun, at the shopping center, and there was only one big street.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "One side was Jewish, and the other side we called it Polish side and Jewish side.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But-- it wasn't officially.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We just made it up for us to go, and only Jewish people were walking this particular side.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Trying to go to the other side, and you can be sure you're going to be kicked around, unless he does not recognize that you're a Jewish girl or Jewish boy.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Otherwise, he's gonna go, hey, you Jew, go back on the other side.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I can write a book, which I did, about the Polish anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Just recently I read about 150 young men and women, Germans, went to Israel to-- to help out.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Goyim, Gentiles, went to Israel to help in the kibbutzim, and helping.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Never would a Polish young guy go to help Israel.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Are you kidding?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then in 19-- like I said, we were from '39 to '41 under the Communist regime. '41 and it was too good to be true.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In '41 they marched into-- when the pact was done by the politicians-- they marched into the part of Poland where I came from.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That [? part ?] includes Rovno.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the hell started.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "OK, we started to have-- there was posters outsides in German and in Polish.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We have to wear arm bands.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We've got it-- I don't remember those little things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We got that-- they-- they [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why do you say [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They arranged a Jew-- Judenrat.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Called Judenrat. 'Juden' is Jewish. 'Rat' is kind of a committee.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Something like that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were just like-- it was just a joke, really.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
